121
00:10:39,837 --> 00:10:44,672
Oh, um, hi.
Uh, I'm... I'm Bart.

122
00:10:44,674 --> 00:10:47,976
My friends, like,
they call me Bart.

123
00:10:47,978 --> 00:10:52,047
I know. I'm Shannon. Duh!

124
