147
00:12:03,453 --> 00:12:05,921
Well, that's me.
See you later, okay?

148
00:12:05,923 --> 00:12:07,790
Hey, Bart,
I got your journal.

149
00:12:07,792 --> 00:12:09,090
Ooh! Kent!

150
00:12:17,802 --> 00:12:20,069
Here. Here you go.
I'm sorry.

151
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:33,382
That's mint.
I didn't know you could draw.

152
00:12:33,384 --> 00:12:35,850
